sequenceDiagram
    participant Index as models-index.yaml<br/>mcp-servers-index.yaml
    participant Extractor as model-extractor CLI<br/>(Go, build-time)
    participant HFCollections as HuggingFace<br/>Collections API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFAPI as HuggingFace<br/>Model API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RHRegistry as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AccessRegistry as registry.access.redhat.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Quay as quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Catalog as Catalog YAML<br/>(output files)
    participant Reporter as metadata-report CLI
    participant DataContainer as Data Container<br/>(UBI9-minimal)
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard

    Note over Index,Catalog: Flow 1: Model Catalog Generation Pipeline

    Index->>Extractor: Read models-index.yaml<br/>(File I/O)
    Extractor->>HFCollections: GET /api/collections/{slug}<br/>Bearer HF_TOKEN<br/>TLS 1.2+
    HFCollections-->>Extractor: Collection models list
    Extractor->>RHRegistry: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>Registry auth<br/>TLS 1.2+
    RHRegistry-->>Extractor: OCI manifest + layers<br/>(model cards)
    Extractor->>HFAPI: GET /api/models/{id}<br/>Bearer HF_TOKEN<br/>TLS 1.2+
    HFAPI-->>Extractor: Model details, README,<br/>YAML frontmatter
    Note over Extractor: Multi-source merge:<br/>HF YAML > HF API > HF tags ><br/>modelcard YAML > modelcard regex ><br/>generated fallbacks
    Extractor->>Catalog: Write models-catalog.yaml<br/>(File I/O)

    Note over Index,Catalog: Flow 2: MCP Server Catalog Generation

    Index->>Extractor: Read mcp-servers-index.yaml<br/>(File I/O)
    Extractor->>AccessRegistry: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>Public access<br/>TLS 1.2+
    AccessRegistry-->>Extractor: MCP server image metadata
    Extractor->>Quay: GET /v2/{repo}/manifests/{tag}<br/>Registry auth<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Quay-->>Extractor: Architecture & timestamp data
    Extractor->>Catalog: Write mcp-servers-catalog.yaml<br/>(File I/O)

    Note over Catalog,Dashboard: Flow 3: Data Container Consumption

    Catalog->>DataContainer: COPY into /app/data/<br/>(Dockerfile.konflux build)
    Reporter->>Catalog: Read catalogs<br/>(File I/O)
    Reporter-->>Reporter: Generate completeness report
    Dashboard->>DataContainer: Volume mount /app/data/<br/>(init container / sidecar)
    DataContainer-->>Dashboard: Catalog YAML files<br/>(filesystem read)
    Note over Dashboard: Display model catalog<br/>to end users via UI
